<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>We Roast Your Name</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
    }
    
    body {
      background-color: #120f1a;
      color: #ff5a5a;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      background-image: 
        linear-gradient(rgba(255, 90, 90, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 90, 90, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 20px 20px;
    }
    
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 800px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      color: #ff5a5a;
      text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #000;
      letter-spacing: -2px;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    h1::after {
      content: "üòàüî•";
      position: absolute;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      bottom: -1.5rem;
      right: 0;
    }
    
    form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    
    input {
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      background-color: #2a2032;
      border: 4px solid #ff5a5a;
      color: #fff;
      outline: none;
    }
    
    input::placeholder {
      color: #7d7d7d;
    }
    
    button {
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      background-color: #ff5a5a;
      border: none;
      color: #120f1a;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 6px #9b0000;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    button:hover {
      background-color: #ff7a7a;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px #9b0000;
    }
    
    button:active {
      transform: translateY(4px);
      box-shadow: 0 2px #9b0000;
    }
    
    .response {
      padding: 2rem;
      background-color: #2a2032;
      border: 4px dashed #ff5a5a;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: left;
      min-height: 200px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .response::before {
      content: "ROAST RESULT:";
      position: absolute;
      top: 0.5rem;
      left: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: #ff5a5a;
    }
    
    .flames {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100px;
      background: linear-gradient(0deg, #ff5a5a 0%, #ff8c42 50%, transparent 100%);
      opacity: 0.2;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    
    .disclaimer {
      background-color: #2a2032;
      border: 2px solid #ff0000;
      color: #ff0000;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      text-align: center;
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px #ff0000;
    }
    
    a {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    a:visited {
      color: #ff5a5a;
    }
    
    a:hover {
      opacity: 0.5;
    }
    
    @keyframes pulse {
      0% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.7; }
      100% { opacity: 1; }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
      form {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>We Roast Your Name</h1>
    <p>By <a href="https://github.com/Haluan157">Haluan</a></p>
    <form action="/" method="POST">
      <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Masukkan nama panjang, misal Budi Solihin" minlength="3" required style="margin-top: 10px" />
      <button>ROASTüòàüî•</button>
    </form>
    <div class="disclaimer">
      ‚ö†Ô∏è DISCLAIMER: Segala kerusakan mental yang terjadi akibat roasting ini bukan tanggung jawab kami. Anda yang meminta, Anda yang menanggung! ‚ö†Ô∏è
    </div>
    <div class="response">
      <%- response %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flames"></div>
</body>
</html>